title: Chomi & David Kim feat. Janne - Find Me (Mrmilkcarton Remix)
description: In his return to Adrenalin Room, Nick Tomassetti a.k.a. Mrmilkcarton delivers a highly musical, cheekily playful remix of Chomi and David Kim's recent hit "Find Me" featuring the smooth vocals of Janne. Filled with the fresh synths and gritty basslines that you would expect from our favorite dairy container, Mrmilkcarton shows exactly how far we can push dance music envelope as he transforms the vibe from the original mix to fit a moodier atmosphere. This is one tune you MUST add to your collection!
